{"title_page": "Voice\u0219ti", "text_new": "{{Infobox Romanian subdivision\n|type                   = commune\n|county                 = V\u00e2lcea\n|population_total       = auto\n|map_caption            = Location in V\u00e2lcea County\n|name=Voice\u0219ti\n|image_map              = Voice\u0219ti en distrikto V\u00e2lcea.png\n|coordinates = {{coord|44|36|N|24|17|E|region:RO|display=it}}\n}}\n'''Voice\u0219ti''' is a [[Commune in Romania|commune]] located in [[V\u00e2lcea County]], [[Romania]]. It is composed of three villages: Tighina, Voice\u0219ti and Voice\u0219tii din Vale.\n\n{{LocalitiesValcea}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Voicesti}}\n[[Category:Communes in V\u00e2lcea County]]\n\n\n{{V\u00e2lcea-geo-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox Romanian subdivision\n|type                   = commune\n|county                 = V\u00e2lcea\n|population_total       = auto\n|map_caption            = Location in V\u00e2lcea County\n|name=Voice\u0219ti\n|image_map=\n|coordinates = {{coord|44|36|N|24|17|E|region:RO|display=it}}\n}}\n'''Voice\u0219ti''' is a [[Commune in Romania|commune]] located in [[V\u00e2lcea County]], [[Romania]]. It is composed of three villages: Tighina, Voice\u0219ti and Voice\u0219tii din Vale.\n\n{{LocalitiesValcea}}\n\n==References==\n{{Reflist}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Voicesti}}\n[[Category:Communes in V\u00e2lcea County]]\n\n\n{{V\u00e2lcea-geo-stub}}\n", "name_user": "Markussep", "label": "safe", "comment": "", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Voice%C8%99ti"}
